title: The Bicycles As-Is EP (2000) 320k MP3
description:
The legendary first EP by The Bicycles. 

Originally released around 1999 or 2000. 

Liner Notes:

Matt  Guitar and Vocals
Drew  Guitar and Vocals

1. The Jam I&#039;m In
2. The Young Raquetball Player
3. Hello Shelly
4. Under The Trees
5. Gold Pieces
6. Let&#039;s Be Together

Gently produced by Dan Bryk at Flabby Road, Mississauga


Matt and Drew are Matt Beckett and Drew Smith, the original two members of the now five-piece Bicycles. These songs show off a more pastoral, folkie side reminiscent of Kings of Convenience or Sufjan Stevens. 

Definitely a treat for fans of the Bicycles&#039; recent bubblegum frosted side!
